        <mxCell id="ov_comp" parent="layer_overlays" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#8C6300;shadow=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;CONTINUOUS COMPLIANCE EVIDENCE POSTURE&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:10px;font-weight:normal&#39;&gt;EU AI Act (Art. 9, 10, 12, 14, 15, 17, 26)  •  DORA (ICT risk, incident reporting, 3rd-party register, TLPT)  •  NIS2 (supply-chain, board accountability, 24h/72h reporting)  •  ISO/IEC 42001 AIMS  •  ISO/IEC 27001/27017/27018  •  GDPR (Art. 32, 44, 35 DPIA)  •  SOC 2 Type II  •  Auditor evidence = Flight Recorder replay&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
